<HEADLINE> Gary Coleman Arrested Over Fines </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Former ``Diff'rent Strokes'' star Gary  
Coleman was arrested for failing to pay $400 in fines for punching 
an autograph seeker. 
</P>
<P>
	The diminutive actor was stopped on July 10 in Monrovia at a  
police drunken driving checkpoint, Lt. James McInerny of the 
Hawthorne Police Department said Friday. 
</P>
