hours before posting $26,000 bail, McInerny said. 
</P>
<P>
	Coleman received a suspended sentence of 90 days in jail after  
pleading no contest in February to allegations he punched an 
autograph seeker. He also was fined and ordered to attend 52 anger 
management sessions. 
  	   	
