<HEADLINE>  Woman Shuttle Captain Nears Launch </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	CAPE CANAVERAL, Fla. (AP) -- The countdown for the launch of  
NASA's first female space shuttle commander was going well today 
and it seemed as though even the weather would cooperate. 
</P>
<P>
