at the resort last year. 
</P>
<P>
	Chapa, 59, also named Hilton in the lawsuit.  
</P>
<P>
	``Hilton tolerates Rodman's behavior because Hilton desires  
Rodman's business,'' her lawsuit claims. 
</P>
<P>
	Hilton spokesman Alan Hopper declined to comment on the  
allegations. 
</P>
<P>
